{"tid":2447584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"數萬緬甸網民怒屌中國：中國駐大使館請離開 不要管我國內政！！","createTime":"2021-03-15T09:28:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T09:52:34.000Z","uid":2054,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6afe958c8fed9dcadb7ea8ea2e27e588b7d9cdfd","tid":2447584,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"中國駐緬甸大使館Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/191612647581463/posts/3770592539683438/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F191612647581463%2Fposts%2F3770592539683438%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=ceed32d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/191612647581463/posts/3770592539683438/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/TTJZZTTWGNC4XBUTCOKONBQ6PI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FTTJZZTTWGNC4XBUTCOKONBQ6PI%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=5c7a607c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FTTJZZTTWGNC4XBUTCOKONBQ6PI%2F&h=ad5c3749\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/TTJZZTTWGNC4XBUTCOKONBQ6PI/</a><br />\n中國駐緬甸大使館在Facebook專頁發表聲明，稱事件性質十分惡劣，要求緬方採取有效措施，制止一切暴力行為，依法查處相關肇事者，確保在緬中國企業和人員的生命和財產安全。<br />\n<br />\n不過大批網民在帖文「洗板」，留言數量超過4.5萬次，而且負評居多，有網民以中文留言「無需中國大使館，離開緬甸」、「你非常好笑。當緬甸有許多人被殺時，你甚麼也沒說，但是當你的中國工廠着火時，你會發聲」。"},{"pid":"36dd45dbcf6ead42e64f358c5e673ca4a9bb1a70","tid":2447584,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"緬甸人留言<br />\n<br />\n这是我国的内政，你们不需要管。而且这不是缅甸人民所造成的，只是士兵与警察烧毁的火灾.<br />\n<br />\nThis is our country's internal affairs, and you don't need to control it.  And this was not caused by the Burmese people, it was just a fire burned by soldiers and police.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#我们不需要中国大使馆请离开<br />\nတရုတ်သံရုံးအလိုမရှိ<br />\nထွက်သွား<br />\nWe don&rsquo;t need the Chinese Embassy, ​<br />\nGET OUT FROM MYANMAR.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nတရုတ်သံရုံး အလိုမရှိ ထွက်သွားပါ<br />\n#chinasupportingmyanmarmilitarycoup <br />\n<br />\n不情願地離開中國大使館"},{"pid":"bb57f7e2e294a5e3c0c8345ca9bd9cad8ed108d6","tid":2447584,"uid":121259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"吳京去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3edf113ba3aa056a1b70dbba8fd5f285a84f3c9","tid":2447584,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb57f7e2e294a5e3c0c8345ca9bd9cad8ed108d6","tid":2447584,"uid":121259,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"吳京去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"奶緊中共鞋底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b64fd13e88a8677c6308eb9ecfe13d295ddd869","tid":2447584,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930d2c68c220e95a9e2926ebcf040950163c247b","tid":2447584,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"21752b2f3c1380048aa070c93e75ec23fdeac6cb","tid":2447584,"uid":129013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"題外話 緬甸d字好似d人仔咁"},{"pid":"ab6048597d442eb69c34afe836ac537e571b6e96","tid":2447584,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"干預別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2197a27eca27b0a77b3dec37f8d6543ec9136f0d","tid":2447584,"uid":53498,"like":0,"d